{
  "texts": [
    "The risk to human connection to these decisions is obvious, if decision-making across AI-enabled autonomous platforms is sped up beyond human cognitive capacities, then loss of SA is inevitable.",
    "From this there is a loss of knowledge and competence required for moral responsibility for decisions made.",
    "Militaries need to consider the human factors of AI-enabled mosaic warfare.",
    "Extensive simulation, training, and exercises with assets ahead of a conflict must occur so that commanders understand the left and right of arc of decisions made in theatre (Devitt, 2023).",
    "Human operators need to feel connected to the technology stack they are responsible for."
  ]
}